ra) R&D department, in which he successfully created and led the companies first combination product systems engineering team. In addition, Chuck has gained extensive medical device product development experience at Baxter Healthcare. He received his BS in bioengineering with a minor in electrical engineering from UIC and earned his ME degree in mechanical and aerospace engineering from the Illinois Institute of Technology. As a UIC alumnus, Chuck is passionate about placing UIC graduates into contract, direct hire, and consulting positions directly after graduation.                    UIC Logo        Engineering Alumni       Contact   851 S. Morgan - SEO Rm. 811  Phone: 3129969422  MWilli60@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 